    ns1:description "This workflow combines SDF files from all fragments into a single dataset and filters to include only the lowest (best) scoring pose for each compound. This file of optimal poses for all ligands is used to compare to a database of Enamine and Chemspace compounds to select the best scoring 500 matches. More info can be found at https://covid19.galaxyproject.org/cheminformatics/" ;
