    ns1:description "Dating the most recent common ancestor (MRCA) of SARS-CoV-2. The workflow is used to extract full length sequences of SARS-CoV-2, tidy up their names in FASTA files, produce a multiple sequences alignment and compute a maximum likelihood tree. More info can be found at https://covid19.galaxyproject.org/genomics/" ;
    ns1:image <https://workflowhub.eu/workflows/5/diagram?version=1> ;
